data.description: PRICE JUST REDUCED to $347,500!  This is an INCREDIBLE value on this beautiful 4 bedroom 3 bath home in Bay County.  This calculates to just $126.46/square foot!  The open floor plan is bright & airy with lots of space.  The updated kitchen and dining area with breakfast bar is the perfect setup for entertaining.  The living area features cathedral-beamed ceilings and lots of natural light.  A stunning spiral staircase in the living room leads to a spacious upstairs bedroom.  The home also features a bonus room off the living area that would be perfect for a home office or study.  A split plan features a large master bedroom and bath on one side of the house, with two additional bedrooms and bathrooms on the other side.  The master en suite has a dressing area with his and hers closets.  A gorgeous bay window in the master is a perfect reading nook with an abundance of natural light.  The backyard is spacious and private with a new privacy fence and a custom firepit area that is ideal for relaxing or entertaining.  Great family home on a cul-de-sac in a great neighborhood!  Price has been drastically reduced to move quickly!
